Package: easynem
Title: An R package for nematode community analysis
Version: 1.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Wang", "Kunguang", , "whkygl@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7384-5002"))
Description: This R package has a built-in Nemaplex database for nematodes, 
    which can be used to search for various nematodes. At the same time, 
    this R package supports various nematode communities and functional 
    analyses such as nematode diversity, maturity index, metabolic footprint, 
    and functional guild.
